        Create an Addon Class Loader
        Parameters:
        addonManager - the addon manager
        file - the addon jar
        addonDescription - the description for the addon
        parent - the parent class loader
        Throws:
        MalformedURLException - if it cannot convert the file to its related URL
        IllegalAccessException - if it cannot create an instance of the main class of the addon
        InvocationTargetException - if the constructor throws an exception
        InstantiationException - if the main class is an abstract class
        NoSuchMethodException - if it cannot find the constructor
        ClassNotFoundException - if the main class is not found
